MILE Privacy Policy

MILE is committed to protecting your privacy.
This privacy & disclainer statement applies only to the services made available by the Manga Reader application.

----------------------
# Personal information
----------------------
This application does not collect or transmit any user's personally identifiable information. 
No personal information is used, stored, secured or disclosed by services this application works with.

--------------------------------------------------
# MILE needs to access your folder
--------------------------------------------------
MILE initializes and maintains a folder named "MILESettings" in your "Documents" folder.
This folder is only used to save your personal settings of this application. 
The personal settings includes server settings and application themes. 
If you uninstall MILE from your device, this folder will not be removed.
If you re-install MILE, this folder can be used to restore your application settings.
MILE does not transmit any of datas in "MILESettings".
MILE does not use any of your datas in your "Documents" folder other than "MILESettings" folder.

----------------------------------------
# MILE needs Internet Connection
----------------------------------------
MILE only use internet for:
- You want to access to website using service supported by MILE.
- You want to download MOD file from website using service supported by MILE.
- Sending application crash report. The error information contains only application information for diagnosing errors 
in the application for the purpose of improving the application and none other.

MILE do not sell, lease, rent or otherwise disclose any data to third parties.

-------------------------------------------
# Report violations or get more information
-------------------------------------------
If you would like to report any violations of this policy or get more information on any app, 
please contact using email: hipro@outlook.com

This policy is subject to change without notice. Please check this page for the latest privacy policy. 
If you disagree with this policy, please discontinue use of the application.
